		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>How do I find a service provider?</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Use our search page to filter by service category, type, car brand, or location. You can also browse providers on the homepage.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Are providers verified?</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Yes. Providers with the verified badge have been vetted by our team. We check their credentials, business registration, and customer reviews before granting verification.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>How do reviews work?</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>After visiting a service provider, you can leave a rating and written review. All reviews are from real customers and are moderated for authenticity.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
